{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji38.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给孙燕的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孙燕\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1957年6月8日）佩君同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月十六日的信收到。已在初中毕业，甚慰。升学的事，我不宜于向学校写信。能否考取，听凭学校。如不能升学，可以在家温课。寄上三百元给你母亲。以后还可寄一些。不要忧虑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年六月八日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]孙燕，学名孙佩君。她的母亲陈玉英曾在毛泽东和杨开慧的家里当保姆。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":8}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":117,"page_end":117},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}